choose_font             Choose an installed font from a list
embed_fonts             Embeds fonts that are listed in the local
                        Fontmap
extrafont               extrafont package
font_addpackage         Add font from an installed package to fonts
                        database
font_import             Import system fonts
font_install            Install a font package and register it in the
                        fonts database
fonts                   Show the fonts that are registered in the font
                        table (and available for embedding)
fonttable               Returns the full font table
loadfonts               Reads the fonttable database and registers
                        those fonts with R
ttf_import              Imports all TrueType fonts in a directory and
                        all subdirectories
